    "We will further evaluate the performance of MSSC in Section V-E.",
    "The column \"Add Comment\" describes the status of the optimization adding comments.",
    "This optimization appends additional semantic information describing the decompiler output instead of changing the code structures, thus owning a higher acceptance rate.",
    "In detail, R_ref gives the optimization suggestion of adding comments for 557 functions in three datasets, of which 555 (99.6%) eventually accept the changes.",
    "The failures are mainly due to the unexpected response from LLM."
